I've been to many , many hookah lounges out here in Las Vegas/Henderson.
Great design , the layout is beautiful and the couches and chairs are made to relax and have a good relaxing smoke session!
The staff is always friendly and helpful picking out flavors to smoke.
My favorite is cactus cooler!
The hookahs are very clean and tall enough to be placed on the floor without being on your table in the way of everything.
Although the food is slow it's great!
Make sure to try the garlic fries, so good!
The hookah is 30$ unlimited for one hookah per two people witch is perfect!
Overall I give this place 5 stars , they need to work on the speed of the food, but I come about 2-3 times a week and I'll keep on coming!

